{"tid":417610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我有批奶粉好平]澳門有藥房出售受水浸影響奶粉　當局正回收並抽樣檢查","createTime":"2017-09-28T23:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T02:58:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd1df3a53f91b4cb540cd52a773afa00485837b","tid":417610,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:30:41.000Z","msg":"澳門衛生局證實，有藥房出售受水浸影響的奶粉，目前正從市場回收和抽取奶粉樣本做質量檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n衛生局晚上發出的新聞稿，並無提及供應商和藥房的名字，只是表示衛生局正跟進有市民在社交網站反映，在澳門某藥房買到受水浸影響的嬰兒奶粉，而調查結果顯示，有供應商將受水浸影響的奶粉供應給某藥房，該供應商目前正進行市場回收。<br />\n<br />\n新聞稿指，衛生局已經抽取樣本進行化驗，同時，將個案通報民政總署食品安全中心跟進，呼籲市民如果發現有藥房出售受水浸污染的奶粉，要拒絕購買，同時向衛生當局舉報。"},{"pid":"0512c2dd0f4200f92a19a87647d5a407ee81ec3b","tid":417610,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02a1fa74c70792ab4819bf6eae35b5ee5c26dc7","tid":417610,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:04:34.000Z","msg":"都係奶粉者"},{"pid":"8d117b8fe49fa0d4aa473f9c516c100cf42a2327","tid":417610,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:05:04.000Z","msg":"邊會知係水浸產品？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a5955e7c72fcf1cc053ff275c15bf9ed137d37","tid":417610,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:06:50.000Z","msg":"奶粉係用水沖架啦<br />\n<br />\n而家沖定je"},{"pid":"f147998b974ba05331bd6cbb229c5ca9ef698f90","tid":417610,"uid":125722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶粉係用水沖架啦<br />\n<br />\n而家沖定je</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4e1e23bdfdac8e72ee17178add127173197b73","tid":417610,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"